---
const { theme = 'modern' } = Astro.props;
---

<div class={`profile-content ${theme}-content`}>
  <div class="header-section">
    <div class="header-content">
      <h1 class={theme === 'retro' ? 'win98-header' : ''}>Alejandro Garcia</h1>
      <h2 class={theme === 'retro' ? 'win98-subheader' : ''}>Software Engineering @<br />Baylor University</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="profile-image-container">
      <img
        src="/profile-image.jpg"
        alt="Alejandro Garcia"
        class="profile-image"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-text">
    <p>Hi! I'm Alex, a Computer Science student at Baylor and a future software engineer with a growing passion for databases and AI. I'm currently exploring research opportunities while building up my portfolio through personal projects and freelance work.</p>

    <p>
      I got into software development because, where I'm from, it's rare â€” there's no CS curriculum back home. That gap drives me. Short term, I'm looking to work in industry and learn from experienced engineers. Long term, I want to build pathways for underrepresented communities to discover and thrive in tech.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of coding, I love reading, watching movies, listening to music, and I've recently taken up golf. I'm actively job hunting, preparing for Baylor's 4+1 program, and working on tools that help people.
    </p>

    {theme === 'retro' ? (
      <div class="newsletter-prompt win98-window">
        <p class="mb-0">You should <a href="/newsletter" class="win98-link">subscribe to my newsletter</a>!</p>
      </div>
    ) : (
      <p>You should <a href="/newsletter">subscribe to my newsletter</a>!</p>
    )}
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .header-section {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .header-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .win98-header {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .win98-subheader {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--win98-blue);
  }

  .profile-image-container {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin-left: 2rem;
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  [data-theme="modern"] .profile-image {
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  [data-theme="retro"] .profile-image-container {
    border: 2px solid;
    border-top-color: #000;
    border-left-color: #000;
    border-right-color: var(--win98-gray-light);
    border-bottom-color: var(--win98-gray-light);
    padding: 4px;
  }

  .content-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .newsletter-prompt {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 8px;
    background: var(--win98-gray);
    border: 2px solid;
    border-top-color: #000;
    border-left-color: #000;
    border-right-color: var(--win98-gray-light);
    border-bottom-color: var(--win98-gray-light);
  }

  .mb-0 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style> 